---
title: Crispy Crumbed Chicken and Sesame Wedges with garlicky green beans and mayo
description: A tangy umami mayo made with soy sauce and red wine vinegar is the perfect thing for dipping Asian-inspired sesame wedges and golden crumbed chicken in. Garlicky green beans add a dose of health and an added taste and texture to this healthy and hearty dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220404_R05_W20_UK_RR3275-3_MB_Main_high-ff0b649e.jpg
